positions.descriptionShort:
- Matrix LED technology: selective hiding of the detected vehicle area, active high beam in remaining segments

- Dynamic flashing light front and rear

- Marker light in conjunction with the optional Night Vision Assistant for pedestrian marking
positions.name: Matrix Package

positions.descriptionShort:
- Reception of digitally broadcasted radio stations according to DAB standard including DAB + and DMB audio

- Display of available additional information, such as Artist, title, cover in the form of a slideshow
positions.name: Digital Audio Broadcasting

positions.descriptionShort: Transfer of selected third-party apps from the smartphone via USB to the MMI display
positions.name: Audi smartphone interface

positions.descriptionShort:
- Support when parking in transverse parking spaces, as well as when parking and parking in parallel parking spaces by appropriate steering maneuvers

- Steering through the system, monitoring the parking process, as well as gear changes, accelerating and braking by the driver

- Please note: The systems only work within system limits and can support the driver. Responsibility and necessary attention on the road remain with the driver
positions.name: Park assist
